This is temporary, it gets better with time, your dopamine is outta whack right now so your brain is telling you you need more meth. Been there, but rather with speed, and after a week the cravings stopped. I know meth is a lot stronger but trust me it gets better every day. If you feel physically fine try exercising or playing video games, anything to pass the time faster.

I usually get a gram, go home, smoke and play video games or listen to music, or anything in general alone. It's normal especially if you're an introvert like me, though sometimes I want to blow my brains out because I feel so alone and miserable. Try not to smoke at home or smoke only after having a conversation/making a friend as positive reinforcement.
